code: @Override @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public byte[] serialize(PyObject element) {     if (this.schema == null) {         try {             this.schema = SerializationUtils.deserializeObject(this.serSchema).         } catch (Exception e) {             throw new FlinkRuntimeException("Schema could not be deserialized.", e).         }     }     return this.schema.serialize(element). }
